Third-Party Components
========================

This project bundles or depends on the following third-party software:

- Taiganet WS4000 Simulator v4 — download from
  https://www.taiganet.com/dlv4new.php?os_type=win&public=1&dl_type=archive
  or https://archive.org/details/ws-4000-simulator-installer
- FMOD (fmod64.dll) — included in the WS4000 simulator bundle
- Wine-GE — https://github.com/GloriousEggroll/wine-ge-custom
- DXVK — installed via winetricks
- gotget/novnc — web VNC sidecar image

The WS4000 simulator binaries are not redistributed in this git repository.
Run `./build/download-ws4000.sh` before building the container image.
